---
title: "_applyAssetParamsUpdates (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: check adds.length and removes.length
    q_check_empty --> q_error_empty: both == 0
    q_error_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_remove_loop: at least one non-empty
    q_remove_loop --> q_check_live_rm: for each asset to remove
    q_check_live_rm --> q_error_live: live auction exists for asset
    q_error_live --> [*]: revert LiveAuction
    q_check_live_rm --> q_check_has_params: no live auction
    q_check_has_params --> q_error_not_set: decimals == 0
    q_error_not_set --> [*]: revert AssetParamsNotSet
    q_check_has_params --> q_delete: params exist
    q_delete --> q_remove_loop: delete s_assetParams[asset]
    q_remove_loop --> q_add_loop: removals done
    q_add_loop --> q_check_live_add: for each asset to add
    q_check_live_add --> q_error_live_add: live auction exists
    q_error_live_add --> [*]: revert LiveAuction
    q_check_live_add --> q_check_allowlisted: no live auction
    q_check_allowlisted --> q_error_not_allowed: !allowlisted(asset)
    q_error_not_allowed --> [*]: revert AssetNotAllowlisted
    q_check_allowlisted --> q_check_decimals: allowlisted
    q_check_decimals --> q_error_decimals: params.decimals != actual decimals
    q_error_decimals --> [*]: revert InvalidAssetDecimals
    q_check_decimals --> q_check_min_size: decimals match
    q_check_min_size --> q_error_zero: minAuctionSizeUsd == 0
    q_error_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue
    q_check_min_size --> q_check_is_out: minAuctionSizeUsd > 0
    q_check_is_out --> q_store: asset == assetOut (skip auction-specific validation)
    q_check_is_out --> q_validate_duration: asset != assetOut
    q_validate_duration --> q_validate_multipliers: validate duration, endingPriceMultiplier, startingPriceMultiplier
    q_validate_multipliers --> q_store: all valid
    q_store --> q_add_loop: s_assetParams[asset] = params
    q_add_loop --> [*]: all adds processed

    note right of q_validate_duration
        INV-001: Cannot modify params during live auctions
        INV-002: Asset must be allowlisted in PriceManager before setting params
        INV-003: Decimals must match on-chain ERC20 decimals
        INV-004: endingPriceMultiplier >= minPriceMultiplier (immutable lower bound)
        INV-005: startingPriceMultiplier >= endingPriceMultiplier
    end note
